OL,3,CFilm buffs flock to historic hall for
OL,4,Cnew guided tours
OL,6,FFilm buffs are being given the chance
OL,7,Fto step onto the set of some of TV and
OL,8,Fcinema's biggest productions as one of
OL,9,FLiverpool's most iconic buildings
OL,10,Flaunches a brand-new series of guided
OL,11,Ffilm tours.
OL,13,FSt George's Hall has doubled as
OL,14,Feverything from the gritty streets of
OL,15,FProhibition-era Birmingham in Peaky
OL,16,FBlinders to the magical world of New
OL,17,FYork in Fantastic Beasts and Where to
OL,18,FFind Them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
