OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782154093
OL,3,CFilm buffs flock to historic hall for
OL,4,Cnew guided tours
OL,6,FNow, in collaboration with the
OL,7,FLiverpool Film Office, the Grade I-
OL,8,Flisted building is opening its doors
OL,9,Fto show movie fans exactly where the
OL,10,FHollywood magic happened.
OL,12,FThe new immersive tours will let
OL,13,Fvisitors explore the building's grand
OL,14,Finteriors, its underground cells, and
OL,15,Fthe historic courtrooms that have
OL,16,Fproven to be an irresistible backdrop
OL,17,Ffor several international filmmakers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
