PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782154093
OL,3,CFilm buffs flock to historic hall for
OL,4,Cnew guided tours
OL,6,FLed by the Hall's expert guides, the
OL,7,Flaunch comes at a time when
OL,8,FLiverpool's status as the "Hollywood
OL,9,Fof the North" is booming.
OL,11,FA recent Impact Report by the
OL,12,FLiverpool Film Office revealed record-
OL,13,Fbreaking growth for the region's
OL,14,Fscreen industry.
OL,16,FSince 2019, more than 1,600
OL,17,Fproductions have filmed in the
OL,18,FLiverpool City Region, injecting a
OL,19,Fmassive #150 million into the local
OL,20,Feconomy and supporting over 5,400 jobs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
