PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782154093
OL,3,CFilm buffs flock to historic hall for
OL,4,Cnew guided tours
OL,6,FOrganisers say the new film tours
OL,7,Frepresent a "bold step" in connecting
OL,8,Fthe building's rich history with the
OL,9,Fmodern pop-culture moments that have
OL,10,Fbrought it to global audiences.
OL,12,FVisitors will discover exclusive
OL,13,Fbehind-the-scenes stories from film
OL,14,Fsets, explore precise locations used
OL,15,Fin pivotal scenes, and see the
OL,16,Fhistoric landmark through a completely
OL,17,Fdifferent lens.
OL,19,FThe inaugural tours launched this
OL,20,Fspring, with further dates set to be
OL,21,Fannounced to meet demand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
